^ "Germany Gains New Specialised Television Channels". INTERSPACE. pp. Section 750.  |access-date= requires |url= (help)
^ "German n-tv minority sale". The Times. London. January 7, 2004. p. 20.  |access-date= requires |url= (help)
^ "Lunch with Rupert not to everyone's taste". Guardian Unlimited. November 9, 2005.  |access-date= requires |url= (help)
^ Borussia Dortmund sale



