Company Overview of Verlag Norman Rentrop GmbH



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Norman   Rentrop  Founder and Owner, Verlag Norman Rentrop GmbHAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships60--
Background

		Mr. Norman Rentrop is Founder and Owner at Verlag Norman Rentrop GmbH. Mr. Rentrop has built the publishing firm into a successful mid-sized enterprise. He has been the Chairman of the Board of Supervisors at VNR Verlag für die Deutsche Wirtschaft AG since 1999 and serves as its Member of Board of Supervisors. He is Publisher and Investor. His first periodical publication is Die Geschäftsidee. He studied Business Management.	
	



